rows.label: tlk41400021_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Nature and greenery are the heart of
Gula! If you're after a souvenir,
make sure it's real Gulan wood!

rows.label: tlk41400021_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Grand, isn't it? If there's one thing
Trigo has over the rest of Gula,
it's the quality of the trees!

rows.label: tlk41400021_01_msg0003
rows.name:
So of course you'll find better wooden
craftwork here than anywhere else in
the land! All of it handmade, too!

rows.label: tlk41400021_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Just take some of these beauties
in your hands. I can guarantee
you'll be smitten!
